parameters:
\SE[50]Um, um... Lunaroa-san...? \SE[95]I need to go to the
bathroom...

\SE[2]Laura... Do you know? \SE[3]When living beings are
in the process of excretion, they become very vulnerable.
\SE[2]Therefore, careless urination is a dangerous
behavior.

\SM[nod]\SE[10]But don't worry. \SM[nod]\SE[10]I will
protect your vulnerable time. [2]There is absolutely no
danger that will come to you.

\SE[95]Um...! C-Can you wait for me outside...!? \SE[31]Even
I, as amazing as I am, am not prepared to be seen while
I'm... doing my business...!!

\SE[0]It's okay. Laura's skirt is long, so \SE[0]it's
well covered and you won't see anything. Don't worry.

\SE[33] (No...! I can't win against Luna with just my
words...)

\SE[58]It might be a little embarrassing to have the sound
of peeing heard...

\SE[0]Alright, let's do this. \SE[0]When Laura is going
to pee, if I flush the toilet, you won't hear the sound,
right?

\SE[2]But, since I don't know when Laura will 'go,' please
let me know when Laura is going to 'pee.'

\SE[7]But... is there any other way...? \SE[3]If it's
okay for Laura to be heard making a sound, \SE[7]I don't
mind, but... [3]What should we do?

\SE[116] (Being heard...!? I haven't really thought about it
much, but it's starting to feel like something
'embarrassing'...!!)

\SM[tremble]\SE[116]Ah... no...!! \SE[31]I really can't take
it anymore...!

\SM[nod]\SE[14]Be brave... Laura...! \SE[57]When you need to
'go,' say I'm going!

\SE[95]Uu... I understand... \SE[51]I'll say it... I'll
brace myself...
Ah... no...! I'm going...! I'll... I'll go...!!

\SE[95]I really... crossed the line... \!\SE[53]There's no
going back now...

\SE[15]Congratulations... Laura...! You did a great job
with your 'pee'! \SE[15]This place is already 'safe'...!
Let's move forward...!
